LocalitiesAutocompleteResponse

Attributes describing a locality. Not all attributes will be available for all locality types.

Field Required Type Description

admin_0

optional string

Contains the country name.

admin_1

optional string

Contains the administrative level including the suggestion.

admin_2

optional string

For small locality type points of interests (suburbs, neighborhoods, villages), contains the municipality it belongs to.

description

optional string

Concatenation of name, admin_1, admin_0 to be used as suggestion in drop down list if needed. The description can vary depending on the type requested.

has_addresses

optional boolean

On the specific territory of United Kingdom, Localities autocomplete request can return the additional attribute has_addresses for a postal code, which indicates if a postal code bears addresses. When has_addresses is true, it is possible to display a list of the available addresses by requesting details with the Localities public_id. To get the details of an address you will need to request again /details endpoint passing in the dedicated address public_id.

locality

optional string

The parent locality when retrieving a POI. often empty.

location

optional object

An object describing a specific location with Latitude and Longitude in decimal degrees.

matched_substrings

optional LocalitiesAutocompleteMatchedFields See LocalitiesAutocompleteMatchedFields for more information.

name

optional string

contains the human-readable name for the returned result. For postal_code results, this is directly the postal code value. For locality results, name in the specified language is returns. If no language is specified, default name (country local language) is returned.

postal_codes

optional Array<string>

Contains an array of known postal codes for a locality (only available on suggestions with country:fr for France or it for Italy and type: locality).

postal_town

optional string

Contains the larger city (or the post office city) for a postal_code (only available on suggestions with type: postal_code).

public_id

optional string

Contains a unique ID for each suggestion. Please use this ID if you need to give us feedbacks on results. This ID is also required to perform Localities Details request.

type

optional LocalitiesTypes See LocalitiesTypes for more information.

viewpoint

optional object

Contains the bounds for the locality
